snippet.textDisplay:
Another glorified aspect of Coke Studio Bangla is the English Subtitle.. It is translated in such a wonderful way! Translating Bangla words into English is already a difficult and delicate artistic matter. Yet the sense of the lyrics of this song has been translated into English in such a wonderful way, getting overwhelmed! This is how our songs are spreading worldwide. The emotions are catching on with everyone. As a student of English Literature, I am able to feel the things well.

But I found out that the subtitles for most of the songs in Coke Studio are written by Srabanti Dutta. Here's something for you - Love! Love!!
